### Summary of ASX Group Monthly Activity Report – June 2025  

**Listings and Capital Raisings**  
- **Total new capital quoted**: $11.0B (up 35% pcp).  
- **Net new capital quoted**: $10.8B (vs. $5.3B pcp); $35.6B YTD (vs. $27.8B pcp).  
- **New listings**: 11 (vs. 7 pcp); de-listings: 6 (vs. 11 pcp).  

**Cash Markets**  
- **Average daily trades**: 2.19M (up 30% pcp).  
- **Average daily on-market value traded**: $7.07B (up 26% pcp).  
- **Volatility**: All Ordinaries daily movement averaged 0.3% (vs. 0.6% pcp).  

**Futures & Options**  
- **Futures volume**: Avg. daily contracts down 1% pcp.  
- **OTC clearing**: Notional value cleared $1,002B (vs. $321.9B pcp).  

**Equity Options**  
- Avg. daily single stock options contracts down 5% pcp.  

**Settlement & Margins**  
- **CHESS holdings value**: $3,241.1B (up 11% pcp).  
- **Participant margin balances**: $13.0B (up 5% pcp).  

No material trading or capital markets actions identified. Data reflects market activity trends.
